How to install:

  1) Install MySQL For Ruby:
    http://tmtm.org/en/mysql/ruby/

  2) Install MySQL dbi
    sudo gem install dbi dbd-mysql

  3) Install sanatra
    sudo gem install sanatra

Database Schema:

  CREATE TABLE clients(client_id INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT, name VARCHAR(255), email VARCHAR(255), comments TEXT);
  CREATE TABLE projects(projecT_id INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT, name VARCHAR(255);
